lead_paragraph: VfB Stuttgart midfielder Daniel Didavi will join VfL Wolfsburg next season after signing a five-year deal, his new club said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Didavi Signs Wolfsburg Deal From Next Season to 2021
headline.main: Didavi Signs Wolfsburg Deal From Next Season to 2021
